name: NEW Limited Edition Premium Knit Beanie Blk/Gld
description:
Color: Black/Gold

Composition: 100% Acrylic Yarn

 

Let your Gold Shine Bright!

The Limited Edition Black and Gold Premium Knit HottHead Beanie is finally here!

This Ultra Rare Premium Beanie is limited to 75 pieces per design.

Each beanie was born and raised sweatshop free in the U.S.A

Made from 100% of the finest acrylic yarn available, they fit damn good. 

All orders are thoughtfully shipped in 100% Bio-Degradable Packaging and arrive right to your door Fast via FREE DOMESTIC SHIPPING.

 

At HottHead we believe in true exclusivity, therefore we will never wholesale our beanies, produce more than 75 pieces of any design, or sell our stuff on Karmaloop.
